Sharing Information with Third Parties
We don’t share or sell your information for commercial purposes. However, all financial companies need to share customers’ personal information to run their everyday business.
In order to most effectively serve you, we use services from established third party payment providers (such as with PLAID TECHNOLOGIES INC, Lithic Inc, Patriot Bank, N.A) to handle credit card transactions and order fulfillment. These companies receive the information needed to verify and authorize your credit card or other payment information and to process and ship your order.
You can access more information regarding the use of data by Patriot Bank, N.A directly on their website through this address.
